Saraakiisha caafimaadka oo ka socda 11 waddan ayaa magaalada Accra ee Ghana ku kulmaya, waxayna ka tashanayaan sidii loo soo afjari lahaa mushkiladan.
Wasiirada caafimaadka ee saddexda waddan ee uu cudurkan ka jiro ayaa waxa ku biiraya saraakiisha caafimaadka ee waddamada deriska la ah ee Ivory Coast, Mali, Guinea Bissau iyo senegal.
