Warka wanaagsan ayaa ah in tallaalka ugu horeeya ee cudurkan la filayo bisha September, waxaana hadda la hayaa 15 daawo oo la arkay in ay wax ka tarayaan viruska.
Maamulka madaxweyne Obama ayaa adeegsanaya lacag kasoo hartay ololihii ka dhanka ahaa cudurka Ebola si loogu adeegsado cilmi baarista Zika.
Balse lacagtaasi ayaa ah qeyb yar oo ka mid ah ku dhawaad 1.9 bilyanka dollar ee laga codsaday Congress-ka Mareykanka si howshaasi loo qabto.
Saraakiisha caafimaadka ayaa sheegay in hadda aan kiisas badan oo Zika ah lagu arkin Mareykanka, balse waxa ay ka digeen in uu ku dhici karo boqolaal kun oo qof oo ku nool jasiiradda Puerto Rico.
