Hay'ada ayaa ugu baaqday deeq bixiyayaasha in ay afar jibaaran dadaaladooda.
Cudurka Ebola ayaa waxa uu galaaftay nolosha in ka badan 2,000 oo qof tan iyo markii lagu arkay Galbeedka Afrika bishii March ee sanadkan.
