Dawladda Maraykanku waxa ay sii kordhisay xadidida ay xadidayso dadka kaga imaanaya wadamada galbeedka Afrika ku yaala ee uu sida aadka ah u saameeyay xanuunka Ebola.
Waaxda arimaha gudaha ee dalka Maraykanka ayaa sheegtay in dadka si toos ah uga soo duulaya wadamada Gini, Sirelyoon iyo Layberiya ee usocda Maraykanka in ay qasab ku tahay in ay kadagaan mid ka mid ah shanta garoon ee baadhitaanada caabuqa Ebola laga fulinayo.
Afhayen u hadashay waaxda arrimaha dibadda ee Maraykanka Marie Harf, ayaa sheegtay in go'aankaas fulintiisa ay bilaabi doonaan arbacada.
