Waxa soo baxaya warar sheegaya in qof kalkaaliya caafimaad ahaa uu ka baxsaday goob lagu karantiilayey shaqaalaha caafimaadka ee uu cudurkan ku dhacay.
Wasiirka war faafinta ayaa sheegay in kalkaaliyaha caafimaadka ee laga shakinayo in uu ku dhacay cudurkan Ebola uu u baxsaday gurigiisa oo ku yaala barriga dalka, sidaasi darteedna laga cabsi qabo in uu halis geliyo nolosha dad badan.
