Dalka Germalka ayaa u sheegay dhamaan muwaadiniintooda marlka laga reebo shaqaalaha caafimaadka in ay isaga soo baxaan dalalka Guinea-Bissau, Sierra Leone iyo Liberia oo ah wadamadda uu faraha ba'an ku hayo cudurkan.
